flowchart LR
    M[Metric correlates with desired outcome] --> T[Metric becomes a target]
    T --> G[Behavior adapts to improve the proxy]
    G --> D[Proxy diverges from true outcome]
    D --> B[Decisions become biased]
    B --> R[Review, redesign, or retire metric]
    R --> M

    GUARD[Guardrails and outcome measures] -. detect divergence .-> D
